234
00:19:50,737 --> 00:19:56,306
During my tenure of the Meffitt School Committee, I introduced changes and presented fresh ideas.

235
00:19:56,887 --> 00:20:01,656
Collectively passed many successful programs along with my committee colleagues.

236
00:20:02,479 --> 00:20:12,908
We approved and implemented changes ranging from technology to building upgrades and educational programs, some utilizing state and federal grants to underwrite the cost.

237
00:20:13,548 --> 00:20:23,897
I have worked and collaborated with local, state, and federal elected officials, appointed to the state local government committee with both Governors Patrick and Governor Baker,

238
00:20:24,577 --> 00:20:26,358
Advocated in Washington, D.C.

239
00:20:26,398 --> 00:20:39,725
for the Massachusetts Federal Relations Network Delegation, meeting with members of Congress, both Democrat and Republican alike, while always having time to meet with our students, parents and teachers and administrators.

240
00:20:40,986 --> 00:20:49,751
Replying honestly to all and keeping true to myself, building consensus along the way, and at times agreeing to disagree.

241
00:20:50,391 --> 00:20:53,533
As a city councilor, I will bring the same positive changes.

242
00:20:54,356 --> 00:21:06,800
We as elected officials need to make the correct, non-partisan decisions on the issues, not based on the party line or a special group, but based on what is beneficial for our city.

243
00:21:07,620 --> 00:21:11,261
We have a master plan, but now it is time to implement it.

244
00:21:11,902 --> 00:21:15,163
