251
00:22:04,262 --> 00:22:06,543
Comprehensive plan to repair our streets,

252
00:22:07,223 --> 00:22:11,965
All the city streets, we need to hold contractors to a higher standard.

253
00:22:12,405 --> 00:22:16,067
They need to return our streets to safe and passable ways.

254
00:22:16,447 --> 00:22:18,368
Anything less is not acceptable.

255
00:22:19,068 --> 00:22:27,552
Making our city into the vibrant, exciting and upcoming city it can and it will become, just as the ones around us.

256
00:22:28,312 --> 00:22:37,646
