00:22:41,091 --> 00:22:43,194
The amount of land in the square has not shrunk.

259
00:22:44,242 --> 00:22:47,123
Our family and community values have not vanished.

260
00:22:47,823 --> 00:22:56,085
I am aware we do not have the amount of land space that other cities have, but with a comprehensive plan, we have enough space to get to the next level.

261
00:22:56,885 --> 00:23:01,267
By doing so, the other jewels of our city will also benefit, such as Haines Square,

262
00:23:03,318 --> 00:23:08,919
West Medford, the Hillside, Wellington, Glenwood, in all our entire city.

263
00:23:09,599 --> 00:23:16,061
Revisit the parking issue, making it sensible for all, providing a more concise and transparent program.

264
00:23:16,501 --> 00:23:17,701
We need to be realistic.

265
00:23:18,322 --> 00:23:24,543
Under these circumstances, things will not change over at night, and it will take time, but it can be done.

266
00:23:25,103 --> 00:23:32,625
We cannot afford for discussions to continue based on who to blame instead of going forward in a positive and a productive manner.

267
00:23:33,385 --> 00:23:36,547
I am a candidate who votes on the issue, not a promise for the vote.

268
00:23:38,748 --> 00:23:40,648
I am a proven candidate.

269
00:23:41,009 --> 00:23:49,793
I have made changes, not just by talking, but by rolling up my sleeves and getting the work done, which in itself makes me a uniquely qualified candidate.

270
00:23:51,113 --> 00:23:56,176
Continue bringing new ideas, integrity, hard work, and passion to the City Council.

271
00:23:56,196 --> 00:23:58,677
It will positively impact our community.

272
00:23:59,017 --> 00:24:01,238
I ask for your trust in me and your vote.

273
00:24:01,877 --> 00:24:03,737
Number 10 on the Medford City ballot.

274
00:24:06,158 --> 00:24:07,058
