367
00:31:49,696 --> 00:31:56,358
I advocated for a complete review of our current zoning laws to encourage smart growth concepts and neighborhood protections.

368
00:31:57,138 --> 00:32:03,120
I proposed a resolution which resulted in an improved emergency preparedness procedures for Method public housing.

369
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:10,444
I supported the hiring of a traffic engineer to review public safety, traffic calming initiatives, and roadway improvements.

370
00:32:11,165 --> 00:32:18,149
As your city councilor, I will continue to support and offer suggestions to reduce the unrelenting airplane noise over our neighborhoods.

371
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:27,175
I offer the resolve which led to the home rule petition to create a charter review commission in order to review ways of improving how city government operates.

372
00:32:28,141 --> 00:32:44,227
