00:33:37,812 --> 00:33:42,394
And how can I improve the lives of my fellow citizens?

385
00:33:42,774 --> 00:33:45,715
And yes, I have an obligation to the people of Meffitt to get it right.

386
00:33:46,976 --> 00:33:50,878
I also would like to thank the Meffitt Firefighters Local 1032,

387
00:33:52,077 --> 00:33:54,258
and the New England Laborers for their endorsement.

388
00:33:54,918 --> 00:33:56,359
I thank you very much for your time tonight.

389
00:33:58,820 --> 00:33:59,940
Thanks, Councilman.

