00:34:20,309 --> 00:34:21,570
I was born and raised in Medford,

394
00:34:22,213 --> 00:34:25,714
My parents are Edward and Susan Lungo, and my sister is Ariana Lungo.

395
00:34:26,494 --> 00:34:27,154
I attended St.

