00:34:27,194 --> 00:34:29,614
Joseph's School, and I graduated from Medford High School in 1998.

397
00:34:30,094 --> 00:34:33,355
I've been a member of the Massachusetts Bar since 2006.

398
00:34:35,395 --> 00:34:43,957
I opened a law practice in Wellington Circle, Medford, over eight years ago with my longtime friend, Kathleen Collins, called the Law Offices of Lungo, Kern, and Collins.

399
00:34:44,897 --> 00:34:51,438
My husband of 10 years, David Kern, is the owner and operator of Boston Physical Therapy and Wellness on Mystic Ave in Medford.

400
00:34:52,453 --> 00:35:01,821
Dave and I are extremely lucky to have three great children and raise them in a city like Medford, Bailey, Calloway, and Cody.

401
00:35:02,962 --> 00:35:09,447
When I first ran for the Medford City Council, I stated that one of the seven should be close to the youth, and now more than ever, that statement is true.

402
00:35:10,248 --> 00:35:20,657
I have fought for and will continue to fight for low class size, for my children and yours, safer security measures within the schools, safer access to the schools,

403
00:35:21,143 --> 00:35:22,624
and better management of the schools.

404
00:35:23,424 --> 00:35:29,127
Medford needs a succession plan for our superintendent of schools, and we need to start a nationwide search now.

405
00:35:30,507 --> 00:35:34,709
I, along with many parents, tried to push for this last year, but the votes were not there.

406
00:35:35,409 --> 00:35:37,250
This needs to be a priority in Medford.

407
00:35:37,911 --> 00:35:40,492
It's time to bring our schools past the middle of the pack.

408
00:35:41,472 --> 00:35:47,575
In the past, I've worked hard to help implement a girls' varsity hockey team, establish an affordable summer camp at Medford High School,

